-- China Sci-Tech to Raise $600 Million in Placing to Pay Loan, Fund Project
-- Joshua Fellman
-- 2010-06-20T12:04:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-20/china-sci-tech-to-raise-600-million-in-placing-to-pay-loan-fund-project.html

          
          
             China Sci-Tech Holdings Ltd. will
raise $600 million through the sale of 23.4 billion shares at 20
Hong Kong cents each, using $380 million to repay bridge
financing and acquisition costs, $170 million for its Mina Justa
project and $50 million for “general corporate purposes.”  
 The company received more than $1 billion of orders for the
placing shares, according to its filing to Hong Kong’s stock
exchange today. China Sci-Tech will resume trading in the city
tomorrow.  
          
          


  


        